            <h3 class="panel-title">STEP 1: Specify the types of manipulation on the genome <a style="cursor: pointer;" id="step1Help"  data-toggle="popover" 
    title="<p4 style='color:#000'>Choose one manipulation:</p4>" data-content="
<p4 style='color:#000'><strong>Gene editing using nickase:</strong> <br/>offset distance (-50 bp, +100 bp).<br/>
<strong>Gene editing using nuclease:<br/></strong> sgRNA is found in exon region <br/>
<strong>Gene repression:<br/></strong> sgRNA is found in (-1500bp- 1500bp) relative to TSS.<br/>
<strong>Gene activation:<br/></strong> sgRNA is found in (0-1500bp) relative to TSS.</p4> <a href='help.jsp#mt' target='_blank'>More...</a><br/><img width='250' src='img/help1-1.jpg'><br/><img width='250' src='img/help1-2.jpg'>"><span  class="glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign" ></span></a></h3>
